rcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我改主意了。你不能留在這裡。現在，立刻送塞茜莉亞前往大教堂。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們就這麼留在大街上......更危險。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，塞茜莉亞。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......？我們剛才不是向著聖像走的嗎，聖像在那邊，艾澤爾哥哥。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們繞一下路。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繞路？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在要去的地方應該是......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安魂教堂。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薩卡茲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我原本打算到大教堂之後，請菲亞梅塔小姐幫忙求情......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "要讓高階執行者監察也好、要讓戍衛隊隨行也好......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只要能確認塞茜莉亞對拉特蘭是安全的......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "能不能，讓塞茜莉亞，在費莉亞下葬之前，去見母親最後一面。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可是，薩卡茲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果塞茜莉亞的父親是薩卡茲......那塞茜莉亞就應該是薩卡茲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她卻獲得了光環......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......我到底是不是在做夢。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果塞茜莉亞只是普通的“例外”......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但她是薩卡茲......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "獲得了光環的薩卡茲，怎麼可能從大教堂走出來......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "就算，就算，她不會被......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她怎麼可能還能離開大教堂......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......即使會被公證所開除，我也要試一試。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "帶塞茜莉亞去安魂教堂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "至少讓她說聲再見。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attr